  "title": "Junior Pharmacy Technician/ Procurement Officer (Pharmaceutical Industry)",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Description:</strong></p><ul><li>Manage inbound and outbound inventory, including receipt of supplier invoices, monitoring stock levels and expiry dates for replenishment, exchanges, and adjustments</li><li>Conduct monthly cycle counts to verify inventory accuracy and resolve discrepancies</li><li>Maintain and utilize inventory management systems and databases</li><li>Coordinate local and international procurement of therapeutic products, medical devices, and consumables</li><li>Follow up on quotation requests from local and overseas customers</li><li>Prepare and process quotations by liaising with suppliers, compiling pricing and markup details, and submitting finalized quotations to customers</li><li>Process customer orders, including preparation of purchase orders to suppliers, invoices, and delivery documentation, as well as packing of orders</li><li>Arrange shipments and coordinate delivery schedules among internal teams, suppliers, and customers</li><li>Procurement of therapeutic products, medical devices, and consumables</li><li>Order Fulfillment and Documentation (purchase orders, invoices, delivery orders)</li><li>Quotation Preparation and Processing</li></ul><p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li>Possess Certified Pharmacy Technician Certification (CPTC) or Diploma in Pharmaceutical Science</li><li>Minimum 2 years of experience as a pharmacy technician.</li><li>Excellent communication and presentation skills</li></ul><p>Interested applicants for the above advertised position(s), please kindly email an updated copy of your resume to: <strong>gs1@talenttradersg.com;</strong></p><p><br /></p><p>EA License No.: 13C6305</p><p>Registration No.: R23117856 CHOE KIN MUN</p><p><br /></p><p>For candidate who applied for the advertised position is deemed to have consented to us that we may collect, use or disclose your personal information for purpose in connection with the services provided by us.</p>",
